XML-FromPerl
============

Generate XML documents using simple Perl data structures.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   XML::LibXML
   Tie::IxHash (optional)

